"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-snoop-dogg-olympic-torch-paris-2024-b2586492.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The hip-hop icon carried the Olympic flame around the streets of a damp Saint-Denis and is also part of American TV coverage of the Games  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 320, \"end\": 328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9968898216609475, \"rank\": 0.0031115001804297693, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Hip-hop legendSnoop Doggsprinkled some celebrity magic on theOlympicstorch relay in Paris as he carried the flame around the streets of Saint-Denis ahead of the opening ceremony later this evening.\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.447362289674305e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sporting a pair of suitably golden trainers, the rapper and actor carried the Olympic flame on a short leg around the Stade de France in the northern Paris suburb on a damp Friday morning.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.447362289674305e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Local mayor Mathieu Hanotinannounced earlier in the weekSnoop Dogg would be part of the relay and locals certainly came out to support.\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A huge cheer erupted as he appeared at the top of a bridge exiting the stadium area, pumping up to the crowds as he made his way down to the Seine to hand on the flame for its final journey along the river.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1151, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999998949255184, \"rank\": 1.0507447126777087e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop (real name Calvin Broadus Jr) expressed his gratitude at the opportunity in an interview on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Calvin Broadus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I look at this as a prestigious honour and something I truly respect.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would have never dreamed of nothing like this,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to be on my best behaviour.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to be on my best athleticism.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will be able to breathe slow to walk fast and hold the torch with a smile on my face, because I realise how prestigious this event is.\\\"\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic torch has crossed France since starting its journey in May, being carried by the great and the good of the celebrity sporting world, including former Arsenal manager Arsene Wenger, F1 driver Charles Leclerc and actress Halle Berry.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3252913819144866e-14, \"text\": \"Olympic torch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\"}, {\"begin\": 1708, \"end\": 1714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9988767240707845, \"rank\": 0.001112632851762683, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arsenal_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999715783, \"rank\": 2.825585198237559e-11, \"text\": \"Arsenal\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arsenal_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arsenal_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ars\\u00e8ne_Wenger\", \"score\": 0.999999999941565, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arsene Wenger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ars\\u00e8ne_Wenger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ars\\u00e8ne_Wenger\"}, {\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"score\": 0.9999999998292424, \"rank\": 1.0168225026858301e-10, \"text\": \"F1\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\"}, {\"begin\": 1881, \"end\": 1896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Leclerc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.704885507525065e-19, \"text\": \"Charles Leclerc\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Leclerc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Leclerc\"}, {\"begin\": 1909, \"end\": 1920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Halle_Berry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Halle Berry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Halle_Berry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Halle_Berry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other carriers of the torch in Saint-Denis on Friday included French actress Laetitia Casta and French rapper MC Solaar.\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1953, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999992693511044, \"rank\": 4.0437092939158814e-07, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1984, \"end\": 1990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.894939376113426, \"rank\": 0.09977008758625916, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1999, \"end\": 2007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laetitia_Corbin_Lee\", \"score\": 0.7975947174815303, \"rank\": 0.2537656965887329, \"text\": \"Laetitia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laetitia_Corbin_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laetitia_Corbin_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2008, \"end\": 2013, \"t